'''大衛·西蒙'''（David Breen Seymour，{{bd|1983年|6月24日}}）是[[紐西蘭|紐西蘭]]的一位政治人物、眾議院議員、[[紐西蘭行動黨|紐西蘭行動黨]]的黨魁<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kiwiblog.co.nz/2014/01/act_decisions.html |title=ACT decisions |publisher=Kiwiblog |date=2014-01-31 |accessdate=2014-03-11 |archive-date=2018-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181212143017/https://www.kiwiblog.co.nz/2014/01/act_decisions.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="nzherald1">{{cite web |url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/nz/news/article.cfm?c_id=1&objectid=11195793 |title=New energy driving Act, says hopeful - National - NZ Herald News |publisher=Nzherald.co.nz |date=2014-02-03 |accessdate=2014-03-11 |archive-date=2019-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191004194150/https://www.nzherald.co.nz/nz/news/article.cfm?c_id=1&objectid=11195793 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他也曾經在加拿大活動。

==个人生活和观点==
===2019年香港反送中运动===
在[[反对逃犯条例修订草案运动|2019年香港反送中运动]]期间，西蒙为新西兰的民主抗议者的权利辩护。他批评{{le|中华人民共和国驻奥克兰总领事馆|Chinese Consulate-General, Auckland|奥克兰中国总领馆}}称赞中国学生的行为，这些学生涉嫌殴打一名参与了2019年7月29日在[[奥克兰大学|奥克兰大学]]竖立[[列侬墙|列侬墙]]的香港学生<ref>{{cite news |last1=Small |first1=Zane |title=ACT leader David Seymour demands Chinese Consulate General explain "encouraging violent behaviour" |url=https://www.newshub.co.nz/home/politics/2019/08/act-leader-david-seymour-demands-chinese-consulate-general-explain-encouraging-violent-behaviour.html |accessdate=2020-10-17 |publisher=Newshub |date=2019-08-05 |archive-date=2020-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022124407/https://www.newshub.co.nz/home/politics/2019/08/act-leader-david-seymour-demands-chinese-consulate-general-explain-encouraging-violent-behaviour.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。西蒙还于2019年8月6日在奥克兰大学的亲香港民主集会上发表讲话<ref>{{cite news |last1=Tan |first1=Lincoln |title=More than 100 gather for Hong Kong protest at the University of Auckland |url=https://www.nzherald.co.nz/nz/news/article.cfm?c_id=1&objectid=12256015 |accessdate=2019-08-07 |newspaper=[[New_Zealand_Herald|New Zealand Herald]] |date=2019-08-06 |archive-date=2019-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190809020307/https://www.nzherald.co.nz/nz/news/article.cfm?c_id=1&objectid=12256015 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Christian |first1=Harrison |title=Hong Kong protesters gather at Auckland University |url=https://www.stuff.co.nz/auckland/114777487/hong-kong-protesters-gather-at-auckland-university |accessdate=2020-10-17 |work=Stuff |date=2019-08-06 |archive-date=2019-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190807000545/https://www.stuff.co.nz/auckland/114777487/hong-kong-protesters-gather-at-auckland-university |dead-url=no }}</ref>。西蒙对言论自由的辩护受到了博主{{le|马丁·轰炸机·布拉德伯里|Martyn "Bomber" Bradbury}}的称赞<ref>{{cite web |last1=Bradbury |first1=Martyn |title=In praise of David Seymour & solidarity with Hong Kong protest at Auckland University today |url=https://thedailyblog.co.nz/2019/08/06/in-praise-of-david-seymour-solidarity-with-hong-kong-protest-at-auckland-university-today/ |website=The Daily Blog |accessdate=2020-10-17 |date=2019-08-06 |archive-date=2019-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190807000840/https://thedailyblog.co.nz/2019/08/06/in-praise-of-david-seymour-solidarity-with-hong-kong-protest-at-auckland-university-today/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

